org.franca.deploymodel.core

Class MappingGenericPropertyAccessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.franca.deploymodel.core.GenericPropertyAccessor
      • org.franca.deploymodel.core.MappingGenericPropertyAccessor
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    FDeployedInterface, FDeployedTypeCollection

    public class MappingGenericPropertyAccessor
extends GenericPropertyAccessor
    A GenericPropertyAccessor that does not access the given EObjects (i.e. the EObjects passed as first argument to the get.. Methods) directly, but the FDElements these EObjects are mapped to by means of an FDMapper.
    If the FDMapper does not provide an actual mapping for a given EObject, this PropertyAccessor will create a Dummy-FDElement in order to access the default-value of it.
    Author:
    holzer
